metadata.name: WATER SPIRITS
metadata.description:
Discover the power of tech-spirituality with "Ancient Future Now," a collection of digital rituals. Generated from prayers and photos inputted by an earth-based spiritual worker, these NFTs act as self-activating software to heal broken bonds with the Elementals and bring harmony. 

Download to your device and use for meditation, promoting healing for yourself and the planet. 

With each purchase, 10% of profits are donated to the Water Protector Legal Collective. 

Embrace your inner technology and offer a gift to Nature with these digital rituals.
